The invention relates to an intelligent leakage protector with wireless communication and metering functions and a control process of the intelligent leakage protector. The intelligent leakage protector comprises a power source, a single chip, a data memory, a wireless communication module, a voltage and current sampling part, a switch-out control part and a circuit breaker part, wherein the data memory and the wireless communication module are in two-way connection with the single chip; the voltage and current sampling part and the switch-out control part are in one-way connection with the circuit breaker part; the circuit breaker part is connected with the switch-out control part; the control process comprises an address application/registration step, an electricity consumption information collection step and a user control step. According to the intelligent leakage protector, the intelligent circuit breaker is taken as the protector in the branches of a power line; the electricity consumption information of each branch is measured, and meanwhile, the intelligent leakage protector, namely a main line controller, is used for receiving the branch information from the intelligent circuit breaker and the information is gathered and sent to a terminal device via an intelligent gateway, and therefore, domestic small-range power line information monitoring is realized.
